Lessphun is an implementation of the Mophun API for Cibyl, "Lessphun
is Mophun". Lessphun is documented on a wiki,

Lessphun: http://spel.bth.se/index.php/Lessphun
Cibyl:    http://spel.bth.se/index.php/Cibyl


Setting up Lessphun
-------------------
1. First setup Cibyl,

   $ cd path_to_cibyl/
   $ source env.sh

2. Then setup Lessphun,

   $ cd path_to_lessphun/
   $ source env.sh

3. You can now compile one of the examples, e.g.,

   $ cd examples/lorminator_dash/
   $ make

4. To run the example, use the Makefile rule 'run':

   $ make run

